---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Our Programmes | HealthPsyche and CareBridge Initiatives">

<!-- HERO -->

<section
  class="relative h-[75vh] bg-cover bg-center"
  style="background-image:url('/images/hero/hero-school.jpg');"
>

  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/65"></div>

  <div
    class="relative z-10 h-full flex items-center justify-center px-8"
  >

    <div class="max-w-5xl text-center">

      <p
        class="uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-green-300 font-semibold mb-6"
      >

        OUR PROGRAMMES

      </p>

      <h1
        class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight"
      >

        Creating Lasting

        <span class="text-green-300">

          Community Impact

        </span>

      </h1>

      <p
        class="mt-10 text-xl text-white leading-10"
      >

        Our programmes improve mental wellbeing, strengthen
        public health, promote inclusive education and equip
        young people with future-ready skills.

      </p>

    </div>

  </div>

</section>

<!-- INTRODUCTION -->

<section class="py-24 bg-white">

  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-8 text-center">

    <h2
      class="text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900"
    >

      Building Healthier Communities

    </h2>

    <p
      class="mt-10 text-lg leading-9 text-gray-700"
    >

      HealthPsyche and CareBridge Initiatives (HPCBI)
      delivers programmes that respond to real community
      needs. Working with schools, government institutions,
      communities and development partners, we promote
      mental wellbeing, public health awareness, inclusive
      education and digital innovation to create sustainable
      positive change.

    </p>

  </div>

</section>

<!-- HEALTHY MINDS, BRIGHTER FUTURES -->

<section class="py-24 bg-slate-50">

  <div
    class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center"
  >

    <div>

      <img
        src="/images/hero/hero-school.jpg"
        alt="Healthy Minds Brighter Futures"
        class="rounded-3xl shadow-2xl w-full object-cover"
      />

    </div>

    <div>

      <p
        class="uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-green-600 font-semibold"
      >

        FLAGSHIP PROGRAMME

      </p>

      <h2
        class="mt-6 text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900"
      >

        Healthy Minds,
        Brighter Futures

      </h2>

      <p
        class="mt-8 text-lg leading-9 text-gray-700"
      >

        Healthy Minds, Brighter Futures is HPCBI's flagship
        school-based programme that equips secondary school
        students with the knowledge, confidence and practical
        skills needed to thrive in today's world.

      </p>

      <p
        class="mt-6 text-lg leading-9 text-gray-700"
      >

        The programme combines mental wellbeing promotion,
        public health education, Artificial Intelligence (AI)
        awareness, digital literacy, career guidance and life
        skills to prepare young people for healthier and more
        productive futures.

      </p>

      <a
        href="/school-impact"
        class="inline-block mt-10 bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700 text-white font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-xl transition"
      >

        Explore the Programme

      </a>

    </div>

  </div>

</section>

<!-- SCHOOL IMPACT -->
<section class="py-24 bg-white">

  <div
    class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center"
  >

    <div>

      <p
        class="uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-green-600 font-semibold"
      >

        EDUCATION IMPACT

      </p>

      <h2
        class="mt-6 text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900"
      >

        School Impact

      </h2>

      <p
        class="mt-8 text-lg leading-9 text-gray-700"
      >

        Our school programmes provide students with practical
        knowledge and life-changing experiences that improve
        mental wellbeing, strengthen public health awareness
        and prepare young people for the future.

      </p>

      <p
        class="mt-6 text-lg leading-9 text-gray-700"
      >

        Working closely with school administrators, teachers
        and education stakeholders, HPCBI has delivered
        engaging learning experiences across secondary schools
        in Lagos State, helping students build confidence,
        resilience and digital readiness.

      </p>

      <a
        href="/school-impact"
        class="inline-block mt-10 bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700 text-white font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-xl transition"
      >

        View School Impact

      </a>

    </div>

    <div>

      <img
        src="/images/hero/hero-school.jpg"
        alt="School Impact"
        class="rounded-3xl shadow-2xl w-full object-cover"
      />

    </div>

  </div>

</section>

<!-- GOVERNMENT CAPACITY BUILDING -->

<section class="py-24 bg-slate-50">

  <div
    class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center"
  >

    <div>

      <img
        src="/images/government/government-training.jpg"
        alt="Government Capacity Building"
        class="rounded-3xl shadow-2xl w-full object-cover"
      />

    </div>

    <div>

      <p
        class="uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-green-600 font-semibold"
      >

        PROFESSIONAL DEVELOPMENT

      </p>

      <h2
        class="mt-6 text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900"
      >

        Government Capacity Building

      </h2>

      <p
        class="mt-8 text-lg leading-9 text-gray-700"
      >

        We partner with government ministries,
        departments and agencies to strengthen workplace
        wellbeing, leadership, emotional intelligence,
        conflict management and organisational performance.

      </p>

      <p
        class="mt-6 text-lg leading-9 text-gray-700"
      >

        Through practical workshops and evidence-based
        training, we equip public servants with the
        knowledge and skills needed to build healthier,
        more productive and people-centred workplaces.

      </p>

      <a
        href="/government-capacity-building"
        class="inline-block mt-10 bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700 text-white font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-xl transition"
      >

        Learn More

      </a>

    </div>

  </div>

</section>

<!-- COMMUNITY MENTAL HEALTH -->

<section class="py-24 bg-white">

  <div
    class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center"
  >

    <div>

      <p
        class="uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-green-600 font-semibold"
      >

        COMMUNITY WELLBEING

      </p>

      <h2
        class="mt-6 text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900"
      >

        Community Mental Health

      </h2>

      <p
        class="mt-8 text-lg leading-9 text-gray-700"
      >

        Healthy communities begin with healthy minds.
        HPCBI works with community leaders, schools,
        families and organisations to increase awareness,
        reduce stigma and promote positive mental wellbeing.

      </p>

      <p
        class="mt-6 text-lg leading-9 text-gray-700"
      >

        Through community outreach, awareness campaigns,
        workshops and public health education, we empower
        individuals with practical knowledge that supports
        healthier lifestyles and stronger communities.

      </p>

      <a
        href="/community-mental-health"
        class="inline-block mt-10 bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700 text-white font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-xl transition"
      >

        Learn More

      </a>

    </div>

    <div>

      <img
        src="/images/community/community-outreach.jpg"
        alt="Community Mental Health"
        class="rounded-3xl shadow-2xl w-full object-cover"
      />

    </div>

  </div>

</section>

<!-- HOW WE DELIVER IMPACT -->

<section class="py-24 bg-slate-50">

  <div
    class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8"
  >

    <div class="text-center">

      <p
        class="uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-green-600 font-semibold"
      >

        OUR APPROACH

      </p>

      <h2
        class="mt-6 text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900"
      >

        How We Deliver Impact

      </h2>

      <p
        class="mt-8 text-lg leading-9 text-gray-700 max-w-4xl mx-auto"
      >

        Every programme is designed to produce measurable,
        sustainable and community-driven results through
        collaboration, innovation and practical action.

      </p>

    </div>

    <div
      class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 mt-20"
    >

      <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-xl p-10 text-center">

        <div class="text-5xl">

          🏫

        </div>

        <h3 class="mt-6 text-2xl font-bold">

          Schools

        </h3>

        <p class="mt-5 text-gray-600 leading-8">

          Delivering engaging programmes that strengthen
          mental wellbeing, public health awareness and
          future-ready skills.

        </p>

      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-xl p-10 text-center">

        <div class="text-5xl">

          🏛️

        </div>

        <h3 class="mt-6 text-2xl font-bold">

          Government

        </h3>

        <p class="mt-5 text-gray-600 leading-8">

          Supporting ministries and public institutions
          through professional development and workplace
          wellbeing initiatives.

        </p>

      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-xl p-10 text-center">

        <div class="text-5xl">

          🤝

        </div>

        <h3 class="mt-6 text-2xl font-bold">

          Communities

        </h3>

        <p class="mt-5 text-gray-600 leading-8">

          Working with community members to improve health,
          wellbeing and social inclusion through outreach
          and education.

        </p>

      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-xl p-10 text-center">

        <div class="text-5xl">

          💡

        </div>

        <h3 class="mt-6 text-2xl font-bold">

          Innovation

        </h3>

        <p class="mt-5 text-gray-600 leading-8">

          Integrating technology, Artificial Intelligence
          and innovative learning methods to expand our
          impact.

        </p>

      </div>

    </div>

  </div>

</section>

<!-- CALL TO ACTION -->

<section
  class="py-24 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-600 to-blue-700"
>

  <div
    class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-8 text-center"
  >

    <h2
      class="text-5xl font-bold text-white"
    >

      Join Us in Building Healthier Communities

    </h2>

    <p
      class="mt-8 text-xl leading-9 text-white"
    >

      Together we can transform lives through mental
      wellbeing, public health, inclusive education and
      innovative community programmes.

    </p>

    <div
      class="mt-12 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-6"
    >

      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="bg-white text-green-700 font-bold px-10 py-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-gray-100 transition"
      >

        Contact Us

      </a>

      <a
        href="/support-our-mission"
        class="bg-green-900 text-white font-bold px-10 py-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-green-800 transition"
      >

        Support Our Mission

      </a>

    </div>

  </div>

</section>

</Layout>